message.body: what are you up to now?
watching it's always sunny and contemplating my imminent demise. what's up with you?
Off work and bored. Can I come watch with you?
not really good day for that.
What is today a good day for?
What I meant was how is any day not good for watching always sunny? Lol
i mean, you can watch it on your own...
You doing okay? You wanna talk?
i'm just really tired, haha. i went back to yoga for the first time in ages and it kicked my ass.
Okay. Well pencil me in for tommorow. And if you change your mind tonight I might take you to kaminskys ;)
uh, i never agreed to anything for tomorrow...
Haha damn you called me out. I'm trying to be sly here!
not gonna happen, sorry bro.
Oh really? What's up?
i just don't want to?
Oh. Thought you might like fun. Guess I was wrong!
Nah just kidding. But seriously. What did I do wrong?
nothing? i'm just not interested...
are you mad or something?
Well. I don't know what to say.
i mean, i think it would be courteous to at least let me know you understand.
I don't understand. It would be courteous of you to give a good reason you don't think I am good enough to just chill out with and get some food or watch tv
But fair enough. :)
I,ll talk to you later. I'm heading to bed. Gnight
awesome conclusion to this discussion. ttyl
I,ll talk to you later. I'm heading to bed. Gnight
